♪ Always laughing, so want to cry ♪

1161
01:34:31,870 --> 01:34:37,830
♪ Something is shining in this empty sky ♪

1162
01:34:38,590 --> 01:34:44,420
♪ I'm always looking for words
that can replace "Thank you." ♪

1163
01:34:45,300 --> 01:34:50,600
